---
title: Middle Eastern Beef Meatballs with honey-Roasted Pumpkin & Coriander Yoghurt
description: Roll up to a tasty dinner with these easy meatballs infused with mild Middle Eastern spices. With colourful side dishes and a creamy yoghurt sauce, this is a tasty and well-rounded meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c19fab9e3f3393b367b5f02-a61a5b3c.jpg
